  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Building a robust, knowledgeable and credible network of African CSOs with a strong collective voice to call for the delivery of sustainable energy access for all.

This work will build on the previous CS Mott grant to build a robust, knowledgeable and credible network of African civil society organisations (CSOs), focusing on strengthening the structure, governance, sustainability and effectiveness of the African Coalition on Sustainable Energy Access (ACSEA).</narrative>
